#--source https://kb.10xgenomics.com/hc/en-us/articles/360042752692-How-can-I-add-SARS-CoV-2-to-the-pre-built-human-GRCh38-reference

We recommend annotating the whole viral genome as a single "gene" with 
the feature type marked as "exon". 
Then, you will append that GTF to the human genes.gtf annotation file. 

#--find sequence to append to genome and make a .txt file saved as GFP.fa
